><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lily-rose-depp-comes-face-to-face-with-death-in-haunting-new-nosferatu-trailer-3798536">Lily-Rose Depp的职位与死亡的死亡面对面，困扰着新的“ Nosferatu”预告片</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
