-Cumberbatch-and-FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch-and-FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch-and-FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch-and-FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch-and-FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch-and-FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Benedict-Cumberbatch">本尼迪克特·坎伯巴奇（Benedict Cumberbatch）</a>和<a href="/artists/FKA-Twigs">FKA树枝</a>已宣布在伦敦Koko的Letters Light筹款活动中宣布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/fka-twigs-cover-interview-2022-caprisongs-godlike-genius-bandlab-nme-awards-3168413">封面上的FKA树枝：“我的方面有很多，以至于世界还没有看到”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Cumberbatch今天（10月1日）宣布为新的全球环境宣传大使，作为伦敦标志性场地Koko注册慈善机构Koko Foundation的一部分。</p><p> BAFTA，Olivier和Emmy屡获殊荣的演员将支持该慈善机构的努力，以帮助确保伦敦能够成为一个更绿色，更可持续的城市。在谈到新闻稿中的角色时，坎伯巴奇说：“我很荣幸成为科科基金会大使，特别关注环境。亲眼目睹基金会在过去几年中悄悄产生的惊人影响一直令人鼓舞，这使卡姆登的真正和持久变化。</p><p>他继续说：“我很兴奋，启发和致力于帮助人们对所做的特殊工作的认识，并继续帮助改善本地，并扩展基金会在全国和世界各地的工作。” </p><figure id="attachment_3798449" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798449" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798449" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="本尼迪克特·康伯巴奇（Benedict Cumberbatch）。信用：出版" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benedict-Cumberbatch.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3798449" class="wp-caption-text">本尼迪克特·康伯巴奇（Benedict Cumberbatch）。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>为了庆祝合作伙伴关系，科科基金会与Letters Live合作主持了一个特别的筹款版，标题为“剧院的夜晚”。该活动将于11月7日举行，并将看到音乐家和艺术家以独特的读物和音乐表演的形式朗读历史或个人信件。 FKA Twigs将加入Cumberbatch，他们将在演出的慈善版以及其他各种知名的嘉宾上阅读一封信。</p><p>特别活动的门票将于本周四（10月3日）当地时间上午9点开始销售。与基金会合作并受益的当地居民将获得一定数量的门票。 <a href="https://koko.seetickets.com/event/letters-live-fundraising-event/koko/3180599" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>，并访问Koko Foundation<a href="http://www.kokofoundation.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站，</a>以捐赠或支持其计划。</p><p> Koko Foundation首席执行官Sophia Pasetti在新闻稿中谈到基金会时说：“基金会诞生于创建真正特别的东西的愿望，是为Koko贡献Koko是其中的一部分；它的环境，年轻人和下一代重要艺术家。 </p><figure id="attachment_3798450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798450" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798450" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="FKA树枝。信用：出版" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FKA-Twigs.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="capt